ณ               ณ  EBBS Message Area Help File  ณ                     ณ
ฦอออออออออออออออฯอออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออฯอออออออออออออออออออออต
ณ [C] Continuous New Messages - Display NEW messages without pausing. ณ
ณ [F] Forward Message Read - Read messages chronologically forward.   ณ
ณ [G] Goodbye/Logoff - Logoff this system and disconnect.             ณ
ณ [H] Message Area Help - This help menu.                             ณ
ณ [M] Main Menu - Jump back to the Main System Menu.                  ณ
ณ [N] Read New Messages - Read all NEW messages since last call.      ณ
ณ [P] Post a Message - Compose and save a message for all to read.    ณ
ณ [S] Scan Message Headers - Display only message header information. ณ
ณ [X] File Transfer Section - Jump to the file transfer section.      ณ
ฦอออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออต
ณ                   EBBS Message Area Tips:                           ณ
ณ                                                                     ณ
ณ 1) FIRST CALL: First time callers should choose READ FORWARD and    ณ
ณ    read only the last 10 or so messages in message areas of         ณ
ณ    interest. This will set your NEW MESSAGES pointer for your next  ณ
ณ    call.                                                            ณ
ณ                                                                     ณ
ณ 2) ENTER: While reading messages, hitting ENTER will abort the      ณ
ณ    reading of the current message and skip to following message.    ณ
ณ                                                                     ณ
ณ 3) SPACE: While reading messages, hitting the SPACE BAR will abort  ณ
ณ    the reading and drop to the READ COMMAND prompt.                 ณ
ณ                                                                     ณ
ณ 4) AUTO-PAUSE: If auto-pause is enabled, EBBS will pause every      ณ
ณ    screenful or so. Be sure to set your SCREEN LINES as desired for ณ
ณ    auto pause to work effectively. ENTER or SPACE will resume.      ณ
ณ                                                                     ณ
ณ 5) MANUAL PAUSE: Hitting s, S, * or Ctrl-S will pause all text      ณ
ณ    outputs. Any key will resume.                                    ณ
ณ                                                                     ณ
ณ 6) IN GENERAL: I suggest callers simply check into prefferred       ณ
ณ    message areas and post, reply & read new messages regularly.     ณ
